<bibRefCitation id="EFEB4B69FF8AFF82E979127DFF7C50A5" author="Jones, J. K., Jr. &amp; C. S. Hood" pageId="10" pageNumber="10" pagination="1 - 32" refId="ref37728" refString="Jones, J. K., Jr., and C. S. Hood. 1993. Synopsis of South American bats of the family Emballonuridae. Occasional Papers of the Museum of Texas Tech University 155: 1 - 32." type="journal article" year="1993">Jones and Hood (1993)</bibRefCitation>
