<bibRefCitation id="EFEB4B69FF8AFF82EA6D129BFD9350A5" author="Simmons, N. B. &amp; R. S. Voss" box="[256,537,1669,1693]" pageId="10" pageNumber="10" pagination="1 - 219" refId="ref42345" refString="Simmons, N. B., and R. S. Voss. 1998. The mammals of Paracou, French Guiana: a Neotropical lowland rainforest fauna. Part 1. Bats. Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History 237: 1 - 219." type="journal article" year="1998">Simmons and Voss (1998)</bibRefCitation>
