<bibRefCitation id="EFEB4B69FF8AFF82E93C129BFF6550F8" author="Taddei, V. A. &amp; B. K. Lim" pageId="10" pageNumber="10" pagination="381 - 386" refId="ref42798" refString="Taddei, V. A., and B. K. Lim. 2010. A new species of Chiroderma (Chiroptera, Phyllostomidae) from Northeastern Brazil. Brazilian Journal of Biology, 70: 381 - 386." type="journal article" year="2010">Lim et al. (2010)</bibRefCitation>
